Appointment Complete
====================

Hi <%= @stylist.name %>,

You've marked the appointment with <%= @customer&.name %> as complete
and recorded the balance as collected in person.

<% if @amount_collected.present? %>Balance collected: <%= number_to_currency(@amount_collected) %>
<% else %>Balance recorded as collected in person.
<% end %>
---
Appointment Details:
  Customer: <%= @customer&.name %>
<% if @appointment.selected_service.present? %>  Service:  <%= @appointment.selected_service %>
<% end %>  Date:     <%= format_datetime(@appointment.time) %>
<% if @appointment.payment_amount.present? %>  Deposit:  <%= number_to_currency(@appointment.payment_amount.to_f * 0.5) %>
<% end %><% if @amount_collected.present? %>  Balance:  <%= number_to_currency(@amount_collected) %>
<% end %>  Booking:  #<%= @appointment.id.to_s.rjust(6, "0") %>

View appointment: <%= appointment_url(@appointment) %>

